<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA522_06_SU_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema522_06_su.css" />
</head>

<body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema522_06_su_0004">
        <section class="title type2">
            <h2 data-head="2" lang="y" class="fraction_box_title">
                <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                    <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                        <div class="operation_box ml_0">
                            <div class="fraction_box">
                                <span>4</span>
                                <span>5</span>
                            </div>
                            <span>&times;</span>
                            <div class="fraction_box">
                                <span>2</span>
                                <span>3</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        를 어떻게 계산하는지 알아봅시다.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </h2>
        </section>

        <section class="contents paging_layout">
            
            <article class="page page_1">
                <h3>
                    <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                        <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                            두 번째 그림에
                            <div class="operation_box">
                                <div class="fraction_box">
                                    <span>4</span>
                                    <span>5</span>
                                </div>
                                &times;
                                <div class="fraction_box">
                                    <span>2</span>
                                    <span>3</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            만큼 빗금( <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA522_06_SU/0004_img01_1.png" alt="">)을 그어 보세요.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </h3>
                <div class="ex_box">
                    <div class="tag" lang="y">한 칸의 크기는<br />
                        얼마일까?</div>

                    <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA522_06_SU/0004_img02.png" alt="">

                    <div class="text abs_1">
                        <span class="fraction_box">
                            <span>4</span>
                            <span>5</span>
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text abs_2">
                        <span class="fraction_box">
                            <span>2</span>
                            <span>3</span>
                        </span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="input_area">
                        <div class="img_box">
                            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA522_06_SU/0004_img02_1.png" alt="">

                            <div class="boolean_count_wrap" data-answer-single="10">
                                <button></button>
                                <button></button>
                                <button></button>
                                <button></button>
                                <button></button>
                                <button></button>
                                <button></button>
                                <button></button>
                                <button></button>
                                <button></button>
                                <button></button>
                                <button></button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_2">
                <h3>
                    <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                        <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                            앞의 그림을 보고
                            <div class="operation_box">
                                <div class="fraction_box">
                                    <span>4</span>
                                    <span>5</span>
                                </div>
                                &times;
                                <div class="fraction_box">
                                    <span>2</span>
                                    <span>3</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            를 구해 보세요.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </h3>
                <div class="img_box">
                    <div class="f32b abs_1">
                        전체를 똑같이<br />
                        <div class="flex align_center justify_center gap_4">
                            <span> 5×3=</span>
                            <!-- 단답형 -->
                            <div class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="right">
                                <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="15" text-align="center"
                                    placeholder=" "></math-field>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        (칸)으로 나누었어.
                    </div>

                    <div class="f32b abs_2">
                        빗금을 그은 부분은<br />
                        <div class="flex align_center justify_center gap_4">
                            <span>4×2=</span>
                            <!-- 단답형 -->
                            <div class="input_wrap" data-hint-position="right">
                                <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="8" text-align="center"
                                    placeholder=" "></math-field>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        (칸)이네. 전체의 얼마라고<br />할 수 있을까?
                    </div>

                    <!-- 단답형 분수식 -->
                    <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap justify_center">
                        <math-field data-answer-single="(8)/(15)" text-align="center" placeholder=" "></math-field>
                        <!--분수식 ex) 15(1)/(2)-->
                        <!-- 매스필드 키패드 입력으로 분수 입력하는경우 정답 표기방법 -->
                        <!-- (분자)/(분모) 형식으로 표시 -->
                        <!-- xx, -:, ⋯ 는 수식 표시 형식으로 표시 각각 곱기호, 나눗셈기호, 중간점3개 -->
                        <!-- 힌트도 같은 형식으로 처리되서 나옴 -->
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_3">
                <h3>
                    <div class="operation_box ml_0">
                        <div class="fraction_box">
                            <span>4</span>
                            <span>5</span>
                        </div>
                        <span>&times;</span>
                        <div class="fraction_box">
                            <span>2</span>
                            <span>3</span>
                        </div>
                        <span>를 계산하는 방법을 알아보세요.</span>
                    </div>
                </h3>
                <div class="img_box">
                    <div class="f32b abs_1">
                        <div class="mixed_fraction align_center">
                            <div class="fraction_box">
                                <span>4</span>
                                <span>5</span>
                            </div>
                            <span>&times;</span>
                            <div class="fraction_box">
                                <span>2</span>
                                <span>3</span>
                            </div>
                            <span>=</span>
                            <div class="fraction_box">
                                <span>4&times;

                                    <!-- 단답형 -->
                                    <div class="input_wrap">
                                        <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="2" text-align="center"
                                            placeholder=" "></math-field>
                                    </div>
                                </span>
                                <span>5&times;

                                    <!-- 단답형 -->
                                    <div class="input_wrap">
                                        <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="3" text-align="center"
                                            placeholder=" "></math-field>
                                    </div>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            <span>=</span>
                            <div class="fraction_box">
                                <span>
                                    <!-- 단답형 -->
                                    <div class="input_wrap">
                                        <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="8" text-align="center"
                                            placeholder=" "></math-field>
                                    </div>
                                </span>
                                <span>
                                    <!-- 단답형 -->
                                    <div class="input_wrap">
                                        <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="15" text-align="center"
                                            placeholder=" "></math-field>
                                    </div>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_4">
                <h3>
                    (진분수)×(진분수)를 계산하는 방법을 이야기해 보세요.
                </h3>
                <div class="input_area">
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                        <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                        <div class="example_box">
                            <p lang="y">
                                분자는 분자끼리, 분모는 분모끼리 곱하여 계산합니다.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_5">
                <div class="summarize_wrap">
                    <div class="summarize">
                        <label lang="y">정리해 볼까요</label>
                        <div>
                            <span lang="y">(진분수)×(진분수)는 분자는</span>
                            <button class="reveal_btn" lang="y">분자</button>
                            <span lang="y" class="small-gap">끼리,</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span lang="y">분모는</span>
                            <button class="reveal_btn" lang="y">분모</button>
                            <span lang="y" class="small-gap">끼리 곱하여 계산합니다.</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>

            <div class="btn_area">
                <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
                <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
                <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
                <button class="btnSubmit" data-submit="true">제출</button>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>

</html>